<?php
return ['messages'=>['#eji-community'=>'#eji-community','#eji-diamonds'=>'#eji-diamonds','#eji-environment'=>'#eji-environment','#eji-metals'=>'#eji-metals','#eji-people'=>'#eji-people','#eji-products'=>'#eji-products','<p>Along the way, we have been monitoring and reviewing our suppliers. The screening is crucial to ensure our suppliers share the same ethical thoughts. We buy most of the diamonds from Sightholder companies and limit our suppliers to only a reasonable number. We know our sources better, we have more confidence in their sourcing operations, and hence our products.</p>'=>'<p>一路走来，我们一直在监控和审查我们的供应商。筛选对于确保我们的供应商具有相同的道德观念至关重要。我们从看货商公司购买大部分钻石，并将供应商数量限制在合理范围内。我们更了解我们的货源，我们对他们的采购业务更有信心，因此对我们的产品也更有信心。   </p>','<p>As a certified member of RJC, we commit to operating our business in accordance with the RJC Code of Practices. We are always aware of the transparency and integrity of our supply chain. Nature offers us precious metals and gems, we make huge effort in ensuring our suppliers with ethical and sustainable sourcing. We believe sustainability is a journey, not a destination. We keep looking for ways, big and small, to be a responsible and sustainable jeweler.</p>'=>'<p>作为RJC的认证成员，EJI一直根据准则运营业务，确保供应链的透明度和完整性。 可持续发展是一段旅程。   我们不断寻找各种方式，努力成为负责任珠宝商，在珠宝行业树立良好榜样，推动整个行业向更可持续的未来迈进。</p>','<p>As one of Hong Kong’s leading fine jewellery manufacturers, we always have a sincere ambition to be an eco-friendly company.  </p><p>And yet, we faced the toughest challenges to meet the international sustainability standards when we started off our journey a couple of years ago -  when Asia was behind in its push towards sustainability compared to other parts of the world, especially in our industry. Despite where we stand at  times of challenge and controversy, we must make an effort to be more environmentally conscious, no matter how small that impact may be.  </p><p>We focus on putting sustainability at the heart of how we run our business to add value to our company. <br />It is our commitment to being sustainable and ethical jeweller.</p>'=>'<p>EJI作为香港领先的高级珠宝制造商之一，一直立志成为环境友好企业。</p><p>这段旅程充满挑战。尤其是亚洲在这方面相较世界其他地区落后。</p><p>尽管如此，我们仍努力于珠宝生产上提高环保意识；将可持续性作为经营核心。</p>','<p>Beyond that, we continue to strive for the best to reduce our impact on the planet. As a pioneer in Hong Kong jewellery manufacturing industry, we believe we are in a unique position to work more sustainably and deliver real impact accross the industry</p>'=>'<p>此外，EJI致力减少对地球的影响。作为香港珠宝制造的领先企业，我们相信可持续运作对整个行业有正面影响。 </p>','<p>Ethical and sustainable sourcing is at the heard of our business.<br />All materials of our responsible jewellery are sourced with the highest ethical standards.</p>'=>'<p>道德和可持续采购是我们业务的核心。<br>我们负责任珠宝的所有材料均按照最高道德标准采购。</p>','<p>If you are considering partnering with us, we strongly encourage you to also follow and implement the requirements set by the RJC Code of Practices.</p><p>For more information about RJC, please visit their website at <a href="https://www.responsiblejewellery.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">www.responsiblejewellery.com</a></p>'=>'<p>为了未来的可持续发展，我们需要在各个方面开始进行改变。</p><p>有关 RJC 的更多信息，请访问其网站<a href="https://www.responsiblejewellery.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">www.responsiblejewellery.com</a>。</p>','<p>In the next stage of our path to sustainability, we will continue to pursue our ambitious sustainability agenda in each of our business operations. We are excited to be part of this journey and we believe every small step we take counts to help us achieve our sustainability goal.</p><p>Together, we aim to bring a thriving future for our industry and for our world.</p>'=>'<p>EJI将继续在每一项业务运作中推进可持续议程。我们相信，每一个小步骤都对实现长久可持续性至关重要。 </p><p>我们将透过与各界通力合作，继续为珠宝业的可持续发展作出贡献。</p>','<p>It all started with the raw materials we use. The most important aspects of ethical jewellery production, transparency and traceability of our supply chain, are extremely complicated and difficult to achieve. The Kimberly Process (KP) is one of the ways to seek conflict-free diamonds, and we recognized we had to do more than that and we started to use Know Your Supplier (KYS) solution to help. Working towards transparency and traceability is a real collaborative effort with our suppliers.</p>'=>'<p>一切从原材料开始——EJI只从参与金伯利流程的已知产地采购钻石。我们确信供应链的透明度和可追溯性，是伦理珠宝生产中最重要的面向。<br>过程中，我们持续监控和评估我们的供应商。小心筛选，以确保我们的供应商拥有相同理念。我们从Sightholder公司购买大部分的钻石，并限制供应商数量。了解原材料来源，令我们对可持续采购及产品品质更有信心。   </p>','<p>Jewellery is a celebration piece of all life’s precious moments to spread joy; a tangible piece of a symbol of family to show love; a sentimental piece that on passes down for generations. Our designs are timeless, and our jewellery is designed for endurance. For us, jewellery can be more than just beautiful. We tried to make a difference to do our business in meaningful ways to give back to our planet. With nothing but a n ethical way in our jewellery production to create sustainable and responsible jewellery.</p>'=>'<p>对EJI来说，珠宝不仅是美丽的象征。通过采用合乎道德的生产方式，我们力求在作品中体现可持续发展的承诺。<br>环保采购是我们的业务核心。 EJI珠宝均以合乎道德的方式采购天然原材料。这不仅体现了我们对环境的承诺，也确保我们的产品合乎社会责任。我们通过小心选择材料来源，致力推动珠宝行业的可持续发展。    </p>','<p>We are committed to minimizing the impact of our business operations on the environment. We noticed one-time event paper invitations and festive greeting cards leave negative impact on the environment. Think about paper pollution, vehicle pollution during mail delivery, detrimental effects and so on. All these harmful ecological impacts will add up over time, and our planet will pay the price. What we are trying to do is - go paperless. And a better way, why not start to reduce our carbon footprint by stopping the use of paper invitations? Going green is not just a trend. Sending a digital event invite is our first step and we need to start making small changes in any way we can to embrace our environmental responsibilities.</p>'=>'<p>我们致力于将业务运营对环境的影响降至最低。我们注意到一次性活动纸质邀请函和节日贺卡对环境产生了负面影响。想想纸张污染、邮件投递过程中的车辆污染、有害影响等等。所有这些有害的生态影响会随着时间的推移而累积，我们的地球将为此付出代价。我们正在努力做的是 - 无纸化。更好的方法是，为什么不通过停止使用纸质邀请函来减少我们的碳足迹呢？环保不仅仅是一种趋势。发送数字活动邀请是我们的第一步，我们需要开始以任何可能的方式做出小改变，以承担我们的环境责任。       </p>','<p>We are committed to positively contributing to our community, aiming to build a better tomorrow for our future generations. We actively take part in a wide range of charitable initiatives, including fund-raising events and visits held by NGOs which share the same vision. We are thrilled to engage with youth as we recognize our youth is the hope of our future. Empowering and engaging the youth through various education programs, like sharing sessions and workshops for students in design institutes, are our fundamental work to care and support our community. We will continue to find new ways to give back to the community and keep inspiring our people to pay kindness forward.</p>'=>'<p>EJI致力回馈社区，积极参与各类慈善活动，望为未来世代建立更好明天。我们非常高兴能与年轻人互动；透过各类教育计划，例如为设计学院学生举办分享会和工作坊，支持年轻人发展。    </p>','<p>We are proud to be both awarded the “Caring Company” presented by Hong Kong Council of Social Service (HKCSS) and “Happy Company Award” for five consecutive years in recognition of our continuous commitment in building happy caring workplace culture and enhancing happiness-at-work level of our people. Fostering a safe and diversified workplace with equity and dignity is crucial. But we go above and beyond - taking committed actions to provide sustainable employment and build a joyous workplace - to attract, retain and motivate our happy employees. We are dedicated to continuing to care for our people, the greatest asset of our business, and grow together. We believe when our people thrive, our business thrives.</p>'=>'<p>EJI连续六年获得香港社会服务联会（HKCSS）颁发的「商界展关怀」和「开心企业」认证，以表扬我们在建立快乐工作文化上的努力。保持一个安全且多元化的工作环境至关重要。我们积极提供可持续的就业机会和愉快工作环境，与员工共同成长。    </p>','<p>We started using certified recycled gold in creating our jewellery pieces from 2019.<br />Creating responsible jewellery is a long arduous journey, especially one made on foot; but we must always remain keenly aware of our responsibilities to the environment. Recycled gold is an extremely effective way to reduce greenhouse gas emissions from mining. We believe the carbon emission savings can be huge. And our hard work paid off - we are proud to be certified as a member of the Responsible Jewellery Council (RJC Certification Number 0000 3707) in 2021.</p>'=>'<p>自2019年起，我们开始使用经过认证的回收金制作珠宝。使用回收金是减少采矿过程中温室气体产生的有效方式，亦可减少碳排放。我们的努力得到了回报——EJI于2021年获得RJC认证（证书号码 0000 3707），确立了我们在可持续珠宝生产的承诺与努力。   </p>','A team committed to excellence.'=>'追求卓越的团队。','Empowering and giving back.'=>'回馈社会。','Ethically sourced, expertly crafted.'=>'道德采购，专业制作。','Going green - Not just a trend.'=>'环保 － 不止是潮流。','Our Community'=>'社区','Our Diamonds'=>'钻石','Our Environment'=>'环境','Our Metals'=>'金属','Our Next AIM'=>'关于未来','Our People'=>'员工','Our Products'=>'EJI 产品','Our Sustainability Journey'=>'我们的可持续发展之旅','Quality is the priority.'=>'品质至上。','RJC Annual Report 2023'=>'RJC 2023 年年度报告','RJC Certificate'=>'RJC 证书','Read More'=>'更多信息','Responsible sourcing is the key.'=>'致力于负责任的采购。','editor-text-editor-02e4d7f'=>'<p>此外，EJI致力减少对地球的影响。作为香港珠宝制造的领先企业，我们相信可持续运作对整个行业有正面影响。 </p>','editor-text-editor-033fb7e'=>'<p>对EJI来说，珠宝不仅是美丽的象征。通过采用合乎道德的生产方式，我们力求在作品中体现可持续发展的承诺。<br>环保采购是我们的业务核心。 EJI珠宝均以合乎道德的方式采购天然原材料。这不仅体现了我们对环境的承诺，也确保我们的产品合乎社会责任。我们通过小心选择材料来源，致力推动珠宝行业的可持续发展。    </p>','editor-text-editor-1bbfa9a'=>'<p>为了未来的可持续发展，我们需要在各个方面开始进行改变。</p><p>有关 RJC 的更多信息，请访问其网站<a href="https://www.responsiblejewellery.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">www.responsiblejewellery.com</a>。</p>','editor-text-editor-32bd8d6'=>'<p>EJI连续六年获得香港社会服务联会（HKCSS）颁发的「商界展关怀」和「开心企业」认证，以表扬我们在建立快乐工作文化上的努力。保持一个安全且多元化的工作环境至关重要。我们积极提供可持续的就业机会和愉快工作环境，与员工共同成长。    </p>','editor-text-editor-493347d'=>'<p>作为RJC的认证成员，EJI一直根据准则运营业务，确保供应链的透明度和完整性。 可持续发展是一段旅程。   我们不断寻找各种方式，努力成为负责任珠宝商，在珠宝行业树立良好榜样，推动整个行业向更可持续的未来迈进。</p>','editor-text-editor-659ca87'=>'<p>自2019年起，我们开始使用经过认证的回收金制作珠宝。使用回收金是减少采矿过程中温室气体产生的有效方式，亦可减少碳排放。我们的努力得到了回报——EJI于2021年获得RJC认证（证书号码 0000 3707），确立了我们在可持续珠宝生产的承诺与努力。   </p>','editor-text-editor-793c979'=>'<p>EJI作为香港领先的高级珠宝制造商之一，一直立志成为环境友好企业。</p><p>这段旅程充满挑战。尤其是亚洲在这方面相较世界其他地区落后。</p><p>尽管如此，我们仍努力于珠宝生产上提高环保意识；将可持续性作为经营核心。</p>','editor-text-editor-797ad5e'=>'<p>一路走来，我们一直在监控和审查我们的供应商。筛选对于确保我们的供应商具有相同的道德观念至关重要。我们从看货商公司购买大部分钻石，并将供应商数量限制在合理范围内。我们更了解我们的货源，我们对他们的采购业务更有信心，因此对我们的产品也更有信心。   </p>','editor-text-editor-9348151'=>'<p>我们致力于将业务运营对环境的影响降至最低。我们注意到一次性活动纸质邀请函和节日贺卡对环境产生了负面影响。想想纸张污染、邮件投递过程中的车辆污染、有害影响等等。所有这些有害的生态影响会随着时间的推移而累积，我们的地球将为此付出代价。我们正在努力做的是 - 无纸化。更好的方法是，为什么不通过停止使用纸质邀请函来减少我们的碳足迹呢？环保不仅仅是一种趋势。发送数字活动邀请是我们的第一步，我们需要开始以任何可能的方式做出小改变，以承担我们的环境责任。       </p>','editor-text-editor-9877af4'=>'<p>EJI致力回馈社区，积极参与各类慈善活动，望为未来世代建立更好明天。我们非常高兴能与年轻人互动；透过各类教育计划，例如为设计学院学生举办分享会和工作坊，支持年轻人发展。    </p>','editor-text-editor-c051955'=>'<p>道德和可持续采购是我们业务的核心。<br>我们负责任珠宝的所有材料均按照最高道德标准采购。</p>','editor-text-editor-c2f0c99'=>'<p>EJI将继续在每一项业务运作中推进可持续议程。我们相信，每一个小步骤都对实现长久可持续性至关重要。 </p><p>我们将透过与各界通力合作，继续为珠宝业的可持续发展作出贡献。</p>','editor-text-editor-ffbdf02'=>'<p>一切从原材料开始——EJI只从参与金伯利流程的已知产地采购钻石。我们确信供应链的透明度和可追溯性，是伦理珠宝生产中最重要的面向。<br>过程中，我们持续监控和评估我们的供应商。小心筛选，以确保我们的供应商拥有相同理念。我们从Sightholder公司购买大部分的钻石，并限制供应商数量。了解原材料来源，令我们对可持续采购及产品品质更有信心。   </p>','https://drive.google.com/file/d/1gVs-pCpwW73rr06fMqMzbkXPLMd_IOyt/view?usp=sharing'=>'https://drive.google.com/file/d/1gVs-pCpwW73rr06fMqMzbkXPLMd_IOyt/view?usp=sharing','https://www.responsiblejewellery.com/member/eji-o-b-elegance-jewellery-international-ltd/'=>'https://www.responsiblejewellery.com/member/eji-o-b-elegance-jewellery-international-ltd/','text-button-13ba83b'=>'更多信息','text-button-41ceaed'=>'更多信息','text-button-6190fbd'=>'更多信息','text-button-61de75c'=>'RJC 证书','text-button-7c09bb3'=>'更多信息','text-button-8e578f7'=>'更多信息','text-button-dd41f2c'=>'RJC 2023 年年度报告','text-button-e01479b'=>'更多信息','title-heading-0b21a91'=>'品质至上。','title-heading-14eb531'=>'金属','title-heading-2c5037f'=>'员工','title-heading-2f0d59c'=>'社区','title-heading-2f6fc0a'=>'环保 － 不止是潮流。','title-heading-3ad5017'=>'员工','title-heading-490a28c'=>'我们的可持续发展之旅','title-heading-66c359e'=>'追求卓越的团队。','title-heading-6830fd9'=>'环境','title-heading-6d05114'=>'回馈社会。','title-heading-7116949'=>'EJI 产品','title-heading-7ae16ad'=>'环境','title-heading-7d68576'=>'道德采购，专业制作。','title-heading-7e323e4'=>'致力于负责任的采购。','title-heading-8b5f2de'=>'钻石','title-heading-9ed4cf8'=>'钻石','title-heading-b752905'=>'金属','title-heading-bedac67'=>'EJI 产品','title-heading-dc4daf8'=>'关于未来','title-heading-e8fb947'=>'社区','url-button-13ba83b'=>'#eji-people','url-button-41ceaed'=>'#eji-diamonds','url-button-6190fbd'=>'#eji-community','url-button-61de75c'=>'https://www.responsiblejewellery.com/member/eji-o-b-elegance-jewellery-international-ltd/','url-button-7c09bb3'=>'#eji-products','url-button-8e578f7'=>'#eji-metals','url-button-dd41f2c'=>'https://drive.google.com/file/d/1gVs-pCpwW73rr06fMqMzbkXPLMd_IOyt/view?usp=sharing','url-button-e01479b'=>'#eji-environment']];
